uk.ac.gla.abbi.abbi_library.utilities

Class UUIDConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.gla.abbi.abbi_library.utilities.UUIDConstants

  • public class UUIDConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the UUID constants (denoting the protocols used by the Android application to connect to and communicate with the ABBI bracelet). The variable names have been optimized to be as self-explanatory as possible.

    Created by Peter Yordanov on 9.7.2015 ã..
